Package com.java.controller.map

Class MapLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.java.controller.map.MapLoader
  • public class MapLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    MapLoader manages the complete map generation operations for the game, in particular it allows user to load the default map, load user's .map file, create map, and edit map.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Arnav Bhardwaj, Karan Dhingra, Ghalia Elkerdi, Sahil Singh Sodhi, Cristian Rodriguez
